channel.description:
Okay, maybe not PURE win, but at least moderate levels of it. [url='https://forums.blackmesasource.com/member.php?u=94']THIS GUY[/url] is who I'm talking about.

If he can make a full year without posting anything, could he maybe have his cockroach poster level changed to "The One Free Man" or something like that?
